description: I placed an ad to sell some wood shelves that I no longer needed. Hot stud Mike came to my house to pick them up. I had to get back to work and because I trusted him, I offered Mike to stay and disassemble them, then leave the money on the table. I also left him my cellphone so he can call my office number once done. Mike put his muscles to work then, instead of paying me, decided to record something steamy hot on my phone...
title: Wood For Wood
